..TEXT:
|Cos@i parlar~... |degno~:  The poet has
Beatrice affirm that it is necessary to "speak" to human kind by
way of the senses and that even the Holy Scriptures and Holy
Church observe this method.  The tenet thus expressed has the
full support, moreover, of Aristotle's philosophy, namely, that
we learn first through sense experience only.
