|e Santa Chiesa~... |sano~: Holy Church, in its
many offices, follows God's way of speaking in Holy Scripture.
But |vi rappresenta~ in this statement seems also to apply to the
paintings, icons, statues, and frescoes which are found in
churches and "speak" to the people through a certain
anthropomorphic imagery.  |e l'altro che Tobia rifece sano~:
Raphael, who restored sight to old Tobit (see Tob. 11:1-15).
All three angels here named are archangels.
